Tailored analysis tables with with baseline transplantation data.

tailored_transplantationbl.Rd

Tailored analysis tables with with baseline transplantation data.

Usage

tailored_transplantationbl(stcs)

Arguments

stcs

A list containing the STCS data frame.

Value

A data frame.

Details

tailored_transplantationbl(): PK: soaskey.

  • 1. soaskey: Identifier of transplantation. Source: Transplantation.

  • 2. patientkey: Identifier of patients. Source: Transplantation.

  • 3. donorkey: Identifier of donors. Source: Transplantation.

  • 4. organ_count: Number of organs in the tpx. Source: Transplantation.

  • 5. tpx: List of organs. Source: Transplantation.

  • 6. tpx_resec: transplantation level Re, Sec. Source: Transplantation.

  • 7. pre_tpxspecific_count: Number of pre-transplantation (tpx specific). Source: Transplantation.

  • 8. tpxspecific_order: Order of transplantation (tpx specific). Source : Transplantation.

  • 9. tpx_order: Order of transplantation. Source: Transplantation.

  • 10. tpx_stcsorder: Order of transplantation within the STCS. Source: Transplantation.

  • 11. abocomp: Blood groups compatibility. Source: Transplantation.

  • 12.-18. hla...mismatch: HLA mismatch. Source: Transplantation.

  • 19. sumhlamismatch: Sum of mismatch. Source: Transplantation.

  • 20. hlaavailable: Number of HLA mismatch available. Source: Transplantation.

  • 21. procedure_provider: Procedure provider. Source: Transplantation.

  • 22. dontype: Donor type. Source: Donor.

  • 23. donrelsubtype: Donor subtype. Source: Donor.

  • 24. identical_twins: Identical twins. Source: Donor.

  • 25. kpd: Kidney paired donation. Source: Donor.

  • 26. altruistic: Altruistic donation. Source: Donor.

  • 27. don_bg: Blood-group of the donor. Source: Donor.

  • 28. don_sex: Sex of the donor. Source: Donor.

  • 29. doncod: Cause of donor death. Source: Donor.

  • 30. doncod_comment: Comment on cause of donor death. Source: Donor.

  • 31. donage: Age of donor. Source: Donor.

  • 32. donage_complete: Calculated age of the donor. Source: Donor.

  • 33. donheight: Donor height. Source: Donor.

  • 34.-44. rec_anti...: (Optional) Recipient Serology. Source: PatientSerology.

  • 45.-55. don_anti...: (Optional) Donor Serology. Source: DonorSerology.

  • 56.-66. combi_anti...: (Optional) Serology combination. Source: derived.
